		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />hey !
<br />The PRG is 2048kb <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />
<br />The CHR is 1024kb .
<br />So nope....no powerpak support.
<br />
<br />Well it plays fine in Nintendulator.
<br />Anyone wanna give it a go?

		

